{
  "3037520": {
    "name": "Heroes For Hire - Try It For Free!",
    "steam_appid": 3037520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/ed8e17970a3a7c11fbf810ebf9dfaf62.avif?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Heroes For Hire is a passive business management game focused around building a dungeon raiding guild from the bottom up with the GuildOS system.   </strong>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Managing a guild is just easy as it sounds like, too. I mean, when running any business, you just have to worry about your employees, your customers, your finances and your living quarters. What could possibly go wrong when you start bringing dungeons, fantasy and magic into the picture, too? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/54f45f6198d3e7d97c34e27b1f3d106b.avif?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=72 /></span>Think you have what it takes to run the number one guild in the county? If so, you can compete in tournaments and competitions with rival guilds to determine who really is Raiders Digest's top guild of the week! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/aa9be68cf00d8760c7b913faee25f976.webp?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/5ddc5e8d855e0359053973aff82f21a3.avif?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Employees are the life blood of any business. After all, how are you going to raid dungeons when you don't have any dungeon raiders on the payroll?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/170732c0d1fc19f7d391828543161237.apng?t=1750880767\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/170732c0d1fc19f7d391828543161237.poster.avif?t=1750880767\" class=\"bb_img\" width=624 height=408 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit and manage a team of heroes with their set of skills, personality and stats to help them during raids and tournaments. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft, buy and find equipment and weaponry that can tie-in roles and niches for the team and guild. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to keep the needs of your employees well met by adjusting their wages, schedule and living quarters. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/aa9be68cf00d8760c7b913faee25f976.webp?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/da51ca20ae51248db877c0134042be3e.avif?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Set up your heroes with the best equipment and items you can find, and go and let them explore some dungeons on their own when they're ready!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/b6808cf3eebc7bab1c6f4e6ac2460956.poster.avif?t=1750880767\" width=672 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/b6808cf3eebc7bab1c6f4e6ac2460956.webm?t=1750880767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make and upgrade your heroes' equipment using materials scavenged in raids and on gathering missions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft the necessary tools needed to help your heroes out on their adventures, such as potions and bombs. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the furniture needed to turn your guild from a shack to a castle fit for a hero of any calibre. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/aa9be68cf00d8760c7b913faee25f976.webp?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=32 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/2d01b2f8d6536165ce6427c625f5eb10.avif?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Of course, there's more to running a guild than just the heroes and finances—there's the guild itself, too!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/e7fea1313946c18c9566af0800e61d1d.apng?t=1750880767\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/e7fea1313946c18c9566af0800e61d1d.poster.avif?t=1750880767\" class=\"bb_img\" width=672 height=480 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your guild's living quarters with furniture that has been bought, found and crafted. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise your guild's reputation to attract more guest merchants and services with stringent housing requirements. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build more rooms to improve the quality of life for your heroes, and unlock some upgrades at the same time. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/aa9be68cf00d8760c7b913faee25f976.webp?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember, there's always room to grow and expand your guild! So... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037520/extras/70830b06c48fc4a4ecbc2c215da1fffa.avif?t=1750880767\" width=631 height=64 /></span></p>",
